"…I need to fight you guys…please"-Flint

Flint is a young cowardly boy...well, cowardly perhaps isn't the right word, more so he lacks confidence. The young lad lived with his father for most of his life until his father took hold of a magical blade. The blade turned him evil, and after attempting to save him, he was unfortunately killed. The poor boy was left alone...I hope he's doing alright.
